name: Escher Exclusive: Too weird to live, too rare to die!

metadata.name: Too weird to live, too rare to die!
metadata.description: Too weird to live, too rare to die! by Arsonic is an art piece that explores the concept of individuality and uniqueness in a world that often favors conformity. Overall, the art piece encourages viewers to embrace their individuality and appreciate the rare and valuable qualities that make us all special.
